data.description: This beautiful single-level home was built in 2017; this home has some amazing features that include 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, a bright and airy open layout floor plan, nice kitchen with an island in the center. Enjoy the private patio and backyard that's perfect for recreation and entertaining or relaxation, located centrally and close to I-17, Sky Harbor Airport & Downtown Phoenix, community parks, and tons of great shopping and dining! Don't miss this gorgeous come and see it!!!!
